        "id": 9229
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-05-12T11:16:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Idea was not to run it on datastore thread, because when that one fires the callback and tries to acquire synchronized (BGPPeer.this), but the BGP/Netty thread currently holds that lock and is making a blocking call to the datastore it could cause a deadlock (This issue was proposed by gemini)",
      "parentUuid": "2fb859ee_623e8d7b",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 516,
        "startChar": 48,
        "endLine": 516,
        "endChar": 101
      },
